text: Indian Range is a historic home at Davidsonville, Anne Arundel County, Maryland. It is a -story frame hip-roofed Carpenter Gothic style country "villa" with board and batten siding, steeply pitched cross gables, and tall, chamfered chimneys. It was built about 1852. It was listed on the National Register of Historic Places in 1986. ==References== ==External links== *, including photo from 1985, at Maryland Historical Trust *Indian Range, Anne Arundel County.
